It's on autopilot!

00:21.200 --> 00:23.200
That means I don't
have to push any buttons!

00:23.040 --> 00:25.320
And, believe me, I tried to push
a <i>lotof different buttons.</i>

00:25.400 --> 00:27.500
Eileen, how close are we
to the rendezvous point?

00:27.600 --> 00:30.740
We should be coming out
of warp right about...

00:30.840 --> 00:32.840
( Beep )
Now!

00:34.720 --> 00:36.380
It's just
empty space.

00:36.480 --> 00:38.180
Maybe Buttons McGee
over here

