to the wrong coordinates.

00:40.480 --> 00:43.620
Wow, Skips, that's a really
insightful name for Rigby.

00:43.720 --> 00:44.700
Thanks.

00:44.800 --> 00:46.540
I been
reading some books.

00:46.640 --> 00:48.640
Wait, what's that?

00:49.480 --> 00:51.180
<i>Computer:</i>
<i>Alpha Dome found.</i>

00:51.280 --> 00:53.500
<i>Piloted by Mary Stone,</i>
<i>John Murrow...</i>

00:53.600 --> 00:54.740
Alpha Dome?

00:54.840 --> 00:56.460
It's the first dome
sent into space.

00:56.560 --> 00:58.580
Yeah, I know.
Then why were you asking?

00:58.680 --> 01:01.140
I wasn't asking.
I was just surprised.

01:01.240 --> 01:03.060
It sounded
like you were asking.

01:03.160 --> 01:04.140
I wasn't asking!

01:04.240 --> 01:06.060
<i>...Steve Mikulski.</i>

01:06.160 --> 01:08.180
<i>Dome status ââ unknown.</i>

01:08.280 --> 01:09.460
