to stop <i>us,too.</i>

01:48.400 --> 01:50.300
( Rustling )
( Screams )

01:50.400 --> 01:52.100
( Whimpers )

01:52.200 --> 01:54.200
( Clucking )
All: Huh?!

01:55.760 --> 01:57.020
( All gasp )

01:57.120 --> 01:58.700
Mordecai and Rigby: Whoa!

01:58.800 --> 02:00.800
Skips: Interesting.

02:01.440 --> 02:03.420
Or "Whoa."
I don't know.

02:03.520 --> 02:04.700
( Gasps )

02:04.800 --> 02:05.700
Visitors!

02:05.800 --> 02:07.100
Visitors, everyone!

02:07.200 --> 02:09.500
( Excited chatter )

02:09.600 --> 02:11.780
