to Alpha Dome for <i>something.</i>

02:46.480 --> 02:47.740
Follow my lead.

02:47.840 --> 02:50.340
( Clears throat )
Excuse me, madam.

02:50.440 --> 02:52.440
Wouldst thou know
where to find

02:51.920 --> 02:53.940
