of this good township?

02:54.040 --> 02:56.340
Why, you're speaking
of our town father,

02:56.440 --> 02:57.780
Silas the Wise.

02:57.880 --> 02:59.020
Praise Silas!

02:59.120 --> 03:00.940
Together:
Praise Silas!

03:01.040 --> 03:03.020
