04:11.160 --> 04:13.140
Consider thyselves
the honored guests

04:13.240 --> 04:15.240
of Silas the Wise.

04:17.840 --> 04:18.980
Hmm.

04:32.360 --> 04:33.500
All: Whoa!

04:33.600 --> 04:35.260
Mordecai:
The Alpha Dome bridge!

04:35.360 --> 04:37.360
This place is a pigsty!

04:38.160 --> 04:41.540
<i>Intruder alert!</i>
<i>Intruder alert!</i>

04:41.640 --> 04:42.620
( All scream )

04:42.720 --> 04:44.020
( All grunt )

04:44.120 --> 04:46.120
( Grunts )

04:47.920 --> 04:49.620
Man, what is up
with this place?!

04:49.720 --> 04:52.120
That computer's gotta know
why were here.

04:57.120 --> 05:00.300
<i>This is Steve Mikulski,</i>
<i>journal entry 4â6â2â7.</i>

05:00.400 --> 05:02.940
<i>It's Day 1 after The Incident.</i>

05:03.040 --> 05:05.040
