<i>to our coordinates.</i>

05:04.960 --> 05:07.820
( All gasp )
What's going on?!

05:07.920 --> 05:10.380
It's a time anomaly!
It's sucking us in!

05:10.480 --> 05:12.220
Redirect power
to stabilizers!

05:12.320 --> 05:14.380
Redirecting!

05:14.480 --> 05:16.500
Hold her steady, Steven.
( Exhales nervously )

05:16.600 --> 05:19.200
Calculating an 80% chance
of getting ripped apart.

05:20.960 --> 05:22.860
90%. 95%.

05:22.960 --> 05:24.180
I don't know
about you guys,

05:24.280 --> 05:26.620
but I'm ready to die
right here with the ship!

05:26.720 --> 05:30.040
<i>Things were looking grim.</i>
( Rapid beeping )

05:31.000 --> 05:32.780
Auxiliary engines now,
Steven!

05:32.880 --> 05:34.500
Steven?!

05:34.600 --> 05:37.580
<i>So...I heroically sprinted</i>
<i>to the timeproof shed.</i>

05:37.680 --> 05:39.500
( Panting )

05:39.600 --> 05:41.600
( Breathing shakily )

05:44.040 --> 05:46.820
<i>When I got out of the shed,</i>
<i>nothing had happened to me,</i>

05:46.920 --> 05:49.820
<i>but everybody else had</i>
<i>regressed to Pilgrim times!</i>

05:49.920 --> 05:51.920
Good morrow!
Good day to you!

05:51.040 --> 05:52.540
Horse and buggy.
Buckle and hat!

05:52.640 --> 05:54.620
<i>Even Captain Stone</i>
<i>remembered nothing.</i>

05:54.720 --> 05:55.740
Good morrow, sir.

05:55.840 --> 05:57.580
What be
your given name, sir?

05:57.680 --> 05:58.740
Uh...

05:58.840 --> 05:59.740
Silas.

05:59.840 --> 06:01.380
Silas the Wise.

06:01.480 --> 06:03.260
<i>Day 2.</i>

06:03.360 --> 06:06.140
<i>I think I'm the smartest person</i>
<i>on the ship or something.</i>

06:06.240 --> 06:07.100
( Music plays )

06:07.200 --> 06:08.060
( All scream )

06:08.160 --> 06:10.380
( Click )
( All scream )

06:10.480 --> 06:11.820
( Yelling )

06:11.920 --> 06:14.020
That's right ââ
