the info we need from them?

06:29.120 --> 06:31.320
<i>We've got to figure out</i>
<i>a way to turn Alpha Dome</i>
<i>back to normal.</i>

06:31.400 --> 06:33.900
Can you guys send me the
coordinates of the time anomaly?

06:34.000 --> 06:36.000
Uh, yeah.
Stand by.

06:37.320 --> 06:38.860
It's not far from here.

06:38.960 --> 06:40.960
If we push them the other way
through the vortex,

06:40.840 --> 06:42.840
it <i>shouldreverse</i>
the time effects

06:42.360 --> 06:44.360
and bring Alpha Dome
back to present day.

06:44.000 --> 06:45.700
Okay.
Eileen, plot the course.

06:45.800 --> 06:47.180
Muscle Man,
you've got the helm.

06:47.280 --> 06:49.180
You guys ââ
get out of Alpha Dome.

06:49.280 --> 06:51.060
Together: Right!
Not so fast!

06:51.160 --> 06:53.340
I've had enough
of your snooping around!

06:53.440 --> 06:55.780
Look, the jig is up,
<i>Steve.</i>

06:55.880 --> 06:57.660
No! Never!

06:57.760 --> 06:59.760
( Grunts )

07:00.560 --> 07:02.460
( Growls )
We'll find him.

07:02.560 --> 07:03.740
There's nowhere to hide.

07:03.840 --> 07:05.380
You won't
get away with this.

07:05.480 --> 07:07.420
I can do
whatever I want.

07:07.520 --> 07:11.460
Let's deal with them
the 1690s way.

07:11.560 --> 07:13.180
( Cheering )
Aw, yeah!

07:13.280 --> 07:15.340
Pilgrimâwitchâtrial
style!

