07:22.000 --> 07:23.100
( All gasp )

07:23.200 --> 07:25.900
Look what I found
amongst their belongings!

07:26.000 --> 07:27.540
Dude!
Why'd you bring that?!

07:27.640 --> 07:29.420
I don't know.
I thought if we had downtime...

07:29.520 --> 07:34.380
By pressing this witch artifact,
this little man jumps!

07:34.480 --> 07:36.340
( All gasp )
Wait a minute.

07:36.440 --> 07:39.420
