07:49.680 --> 07:51.420
Witch!
Wallace is a witch!

07:51.520 --> 07:53.820
No, I ââ
( All chanting "Witch!" )

07:53.920 --> 07:56.660
Where is the final unbeliever?
Show yourself!

07:56.760 --> 07:58.980
( Growls )
<i>Benson: Skips! Skips, come in!</i>

07:59.080 --> 08:01.080
Where are we
in saving Mordecai and Rigby?

08:00.520 --> 08:01.940
<i>Working on it!</i>

08:02.040 --> 08:04.040
Okay. We're gonna move the domes
into position.

08:03.960 --> 08:05.960
Begin maneuvers.
Eileen: Got it.

08:07.720 --> 08:10.180
( Yelling )
Now, with a flash
of my future laser,

08:10.280 --> 08:12.420
I signal the execution
of these ââ

08:12.520 --> 08:13.460
( Crash )
