My!
The heavens are shaking!

08:18.280 --> 08:19.620
These are witch tremors!

08:19.720 --> 08:21.660
It's a sign!
They <i>arewitches!</i>

08:21.760 --> 08:22.980
( Yelling )

08:23.080 --> 08:24.580
Yeah, you're right!

08:24.680 --> 08:25.980
( Weapon charging )

08:26.080 --> 08:28.080
Huh?!

08:28.800 --> 08:31.140
Quit trying
to laser my friends!

08:31.240 --> 08:33.600
( Screaming )

08:35.080 --> 08:37.080
Both: Skips!

08:37.840 --> 08:40.260
To the escape pod!

08:40.360 --> 08:42.360
( Growls )

