( Laughing evilly )

09:31.560 --> 09:32.420
( Growls )

09:32.520 --> 09:34.900
Aah!
No, no! Stop!

09:35.000 --> 09:38.160
( All screaming )

09:39.360 --> 09:41.360
( All coughing )

09:44.840 --> 09:45.580
No!

